  "title": "Workplace Safety and health Officer for Building & Construction Specific",
  "description": "<p>We’re Hiring: <strong>Workplace Safety and health Officer for Building & Construction Specific</strong></p><p>Working Hours: Mon to Fri- <strong>5 days a week</strong> / 8Am to 6Pm</p><p>Start Date: Immediate</p><p><strong>*Job Description: *</strong></p><p>· To assist Safety Manager on all safety, health, environmental, and welfare matters, to ensure the Project complies with its statutory obligations, safety requirements, and aerodrome safety standards.</p><p>· To be responsible for health, safety, and environmental control, and to assist Safety Manager to ensure that all works adhere to the procedures and instructions.</p><p>· To assist Safety Manager in liaising and co-ordinate with stakeholders, authorities and agencies and other Consultants employed by Developer.</p><p>· To put up daily situation reports.</p><p>· Ensure risk assessment and safe working procedures are correctly executed on-site.</p><p>· To conduct daily health, safety, and environmental inspections, prepare reports and follow up with Project Safety Team / Contractors for closure.</p><p>· To carry out investigations into all accidents and near-miss incidents and to record the findings on the relevant forms.</p><p>· Wear appropriate personal protective clothing/equipment and observe all safety requirements/procedures.</p><p>· To implement and monitor appropriate safety measures in accordance with the Workplace Health and Safety Act and Safety Management System.</p><p>· To highlight areas where training/certification is required to meet the standards imposed by Legislation, Approved Codes of Practice, or H.S.E. guidance</p><p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p><p>· <strong>At least 6 years relevant experience in the construction industry preferably 2 years with the developer/main contractor.</strong></p><p>· <strong>Must be a registered Workplace Safety and Health Officer with MOM.</strong></p><p>· Has developed a Risk Management Implementation Plan (bizSAFE Level 2) or equivalent<br />· Please Note this is for one of the Topmost Client.</p>",
